{"tid":2360394,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"那年二十","createTime":"2021-01-09T16:51:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T17:54:36.000Z","uid":313974,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f6088ab12e996b3816e2e3a0303c79cdcce12728","tid":2360394,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T16:51:28.000Z","msg":"老死話我預成世A0<br />\n不如試吓叫雞<br />\n之後我真係去<br />\n記得你係住佐敦<br />\n嗰晚好大風<br />\n同今晚一樣咁凍<br />\n廣東話未係好正<br />\n不過你教我講泰文嘅樣<br />\n真係好得意<br />\n個身都好香<br />\n同澳寶唔係一回事<br />\n<br />\n走嗰陣時你同我講<br />\n我咁後生<br />\n唔好再有下一次<br />\n正正經經搵個女朋友<br />\n我話我應承你<br />\n<br />\n咁多年過咗<br />\n男仔已經變咗做男人<br />\n我聽日要結婚喇<br />\n老死無啦啦搵我<br />\n問我記唔記得第一次叫嗰隻雞<br />\n我想講你唔係雞<br />\n但係最終我冇講到"},{"pid":"fa3a652e1c5d9b5ba494aaecf853dff570ed2005","tid":2360394,"uid":98338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T16:58:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc889eb89dabcc9274c76b0e4ec8cd317696e3e1","tid":2360394,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T17:06:35.000Z","msg":"瑁 新婚快樂"},{"pid":"47e1a6db7ed125fbc4cae6294527ea597a12feb1","tid":2360394,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc889eb89dabcc9274c76b0e4ec8cd317696e3e1","tid":2360394,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T17:06:35.000Z","msg":"瑁 新婚快樂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T17:33:22.000Z","msg":"弘我見到你貓"},{"pid":"66003d248ed3a06445348d27d03368c94d3febad","tid":2360394,"uid":15473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T17:33:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0bd97fd9e509697c6ee6141486a8be9f06f19e9","tid":2360394,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47e1a6db7ed125fbc4cae6294527ea597a12feb1","tid":2360394,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc889eb89dabcc9274c76b0e4ec8cd317696e3e1","tid":2360394,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":